snippet: The Golden State Warriors played one of their most dominant quarters to start the game, building a 25-point lead. Then, there were turnovers and second chances for Toronto and they had to hold off the Raptors at the end....
lead_paragraph: The Golden State Warriors played one of their most dominant quarters to start the game, building a 25-point lead. Then, there were turnovers and second chances for Toronto and they had to hold off the Raptors at the end.

headline.main: Durant, Warriors Deliver Down Stretch to Hold Off Raptors
headline.print_headline: Durant, Warriors Deliver Down Stretch to Hold Off Raptors
